{"product_id":"nurme-neroli-purifying-cream-cleanser-200ml","title":"NURME Neroli Purifying Cream Cleanser 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eA natural cleansing cream-foam enriched with softening and exfoliating neroli and passion fruit extracts, suitable for all skin types. It is rich in vitamins C and E, revitalizing your skin. The creamy formula contains fruit vitamins A and C, protecting your skin from environmental pollutants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNeroli oil, derived from bitter orange blossoms, has powerful antimicrobial and antibacterial properties, making it ideal for acne-prone skin. It regulates sebum production, balancing oily skin. High in antioxidants and vitamin E, neroli oil combats free radicals, reducing acne inflammation and redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNurme is committed to continuously improving the impact of its products throughout their lifecycle. Packaged in arecyclable PET bottle, it is lightweight to reduce carbon emissions during transport.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMassage a small amount of the product all over the face, rinse with water. Avoid contact with eyes.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Aqua*, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Flower Water*, Coco-Glucoside**, Passiflora Edulis Seed Oil*, Glycerin**, Cocamidopropyl Betaine**, Betain**, Sodium Levulinate**, Lactic Acid**, CI 77891**, Xanthan Gum**, Hectorite**, Cellulose**, Sodium Anisate**, Tocopherol**, Panthenol*, Mica**, Citrus Aurantium Flower Oil*, Benzyl Alcohol**, Passiflora Incarnata Extract*, Linalool***, Sodium Benzoate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Limonene***, Sodium Citrate**.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e* Natural origin\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e** Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e***Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915849568583,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-neroli-purifying-cream-cleanser-200ml-285031.jpg?v=1739897168","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-neroli-purifying-cream-cleanser-200ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}